+
+`pala backup drive` writes a redacted package to a local folder. Use a Google Drive sync folder as the target when cloud upload is desired.
+
+| Control | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--target` | Choose backup folder |
+| `PALA_DRIVE_BACKUP_PATH` | Set default Drive backup folder |
+| redaction | Avoid copying common secrets into the backup package |
+
+This is not yet a direct Google Drive API upload.
